Bundled third-party libraries for local-only markdown preview rendering.
These files are loaded by WKWebView from the app bundle. Zero network calls.

mermaid.min.js
  Library: Mermaid (https://mermaid.js.org)
  License: MIT
  Version: 11.x

katex.min.js, katex.min.css, katex-auto-render.min.js
  Library: KaTeX (https://katex.org)
  License: MIT
  Version: 0.16.x
